\begin_inset Formula $P(B\cap C)\neq P(B)P(C)$
\end_inset

.
 Under these conditions 
\begin_inset Formula $A,B$
\end_inset

 and 
\begin_inset Formula $C$
\end_inset

 are not mutually independent.
