 events 
\begin_inset Formula $B_{1},B_{2},\dots,B_{n}$
\end_inset

 that are collectively exhaustive (i.e.
 
\begin_inset Formula $\bigcup B_{i}$
\end_inset


\begin_inset Formula $=$
