\begin_layout Standard
Let 
\begin_inset Formula $B$
\end_inset

 an event and 
\begin_inset Formula $S'=\{B,\bar{B}\}$
\end_inset

 the corresponding event space.
 For any event 
\begin_inset Formula $A$
\end_inset


\begin_inset Formula 
\[
